text: Horrible planning. Had me come all the way down from Sengkang for an 830am appointment only for me to see a piece of paper on the guardroom glass saying ‘the dentist is not in, please reschedule your appointment’. Quite unacceptable in my opinion.

author_name: Adam Faiq Ataillah Bin Nor Salman (Adam)
text: The medics here are very helpful and makes patients feel very comfortable.
